BN IU KHON V IU KIN CHUNG
Bn iu Khon V iu Kin Chung c Cng ty Ti chnh TNHH HD SAISON (Bn Cho Vay) cng b
cng khai ti tr s chnh, chi nhnh, im gii thiu dch v v website www.hdsaison.com.vn ca Bn Cho Vay
p dng chung cho Bn Vay i vi tt c cc sn phm cho vay tiu dng ca Bn Cho Vay tng thi k (bao
gm Ngnh hng Xe my [MC-SV-EB-EC], in my [ED-OL], Tin mt [CL-FS], Dch v [TP-SL-WD]).
Bn iu Khon V iu Kin Chung l mt phn khng tch ri ca Hp ng Tn Dng gia Bn Cho Vay
v Bn Vay theo tng sn phm cho vay tiu dng. Bng vic k xc nhn ti Hp ng Tn Dng, Bn Vay
ng rng c, hiu, chp nhn tun th cc quy nh ti Bn iu Khon V iu Kin Chung ny.
1. Mt s nh ngha v gii thch
1.1. Bn Cho Vay l cng ty c thng tin nh nu ti Mc 2 ca Hp ng Tn Dng.
1.2. Bn Vay l c nhn c thng tin nh nu ti Mc 1 ca Hp ng Tn Dng.
1.3. Khon Cp Vn l khon tin bng ng Vit Nam do Bn Cho Vay cp cho Bn Vay nh nu ti Mc
5.1 ca Hp ng Tn Dng.
1.4. Khon N l khon tin m Bn Vay c ngha v thanh ton cho Bn Cho Vay theo quy nh ti Hp
ng Tn Dng, ti bt k thi im no, bao gm nhng khng gii hn (cc) Khon Thanh Ton Hng
Thng, ph, pht cha thanh ton ti thi im .
1.5. Khon Thanh Ton Hng Thng l khon tin Bn Vay hon tr Bn Cho Vay mi thng vo ngy v
theo thi hn c quy nh ti Mc 5 ca Hp ng Tn Dng. Khon Thanh Ton Hng Thng s bao
gm gc, li, Ph Bo Him (nu c) v Ph Chuyn Tin c quy nh ti Hp ng Tn Dng.
1.6. Khon Vay l khon tin m Bn Vay phi thanh ton cho Bn Cho Vay bao gm Khon Cp Vn v
Tin Li
1.7. Hp ng Tn Dng l tha thun gia Bn Vay v Bn Cho Vay lin quan n Khon Vay v cc ph
lc, sa i, b sung c Bn Vay v Bn Cho Vay ng bng vn bn.
1.8. Ngh Cp Tn Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T l vn bn ngh ca Bn Vay
lin quan n Khon Vay, ng thi l tha thun gia Bn Vay v Bn Cho Vay lin quan n vic Bn
Vay ng s dng Dch v in t do Bn Cho Vay cung cp tng thi k v cc ph lc, sa i, b
sung c Bn Vay v Bn Cho Vay ng bng vn bn hoc c Bn Cho Vay thng bo tng thi
k.

1.9. Ph Bo Him l s tin m Bn Vay thanh ton cho cng ty bo him tham gia (cc) sn phm bo
him quy nh ti Mc 2.4 ca Ngh Cp Tn Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T
(khng bao gm Sn Phm c Ti Tr l bo him).
1.10. S Hp ng l s Hp ng Tn Dng nu ti phn u ca Hp ng Tn Dng.
1.11. S Hng Dn Thanh Ton l ti liu hng dn cho Bn Vay cc phng thc thanh ton Khon N
cho Bn Cho Vay thng qua cc knh thanh ton. S Hng Dn Thanh Ton c nh km Hp ng
Tn Dng v l mt phn khng tch ri ca Hp ng Tn Dng. Trong trng hp c s khng thng
nht ni dung gia S Hng Dn Thanh Ton v Hp ng Tn Dng hoc Ngh Cp Tn Dng
Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T th Hp ng Tn Dng s c u tin p dng.
1.12. Tin Li l khon tin Bn Vay thanh ton cho Bn Cho Vay, c tnh trn c s d n gim dn.
1.13. Thu l thu gi tr gia tng hoc cc loi thu khc theo quy nh ca php lut Vit Nam.
1.14. VN l ng Vit Nam, ng tin c s dng cho vay theo Hp ng Tn Dng.
1.15. Du phn cch: Nhm thng nht mt nguyn tc ghi s ti Hp ng Tn Dng, Bn Cho Vay s dng
du phy (,) sau ch s hng nghn, triu; v s dng du chm (.) sau ch s hng n v.
2. Phng thc thanh ton cho Bn Cho Vay
2.1. Bn Vay la chn phng thc thanh ton v chu trch nhim thc hin ng theo hng dn ca S
Hng Dn Thanh Ton. Mi ln thanh ton v chi tr Khon Thanh Ton Hng Thng, Bn Vay phi
ghi r v chnh xc S Hp ng. Trong trng hp Bn Vay khng ghi chnh xc S Hp ng, Bn
Vay c ngha v phi thng bo ngay cho Bn Cho Vay trnh bt k sai st hoc thanh ton sai Hp
ng Tn Dng.
2.2. Nhm h tr Bn Vay thc hin thanh ton Khon Thanh Ton Hng Thng ng hn, Bn Cho Vay c
th gi in v/hoc nhn tin cho Bn Vay nhc Bn Vay v ngy n hn thanh ton. Nu Bn Vay
khng thanh ton hoc thanh ton khng y Khon Thanh Ton Hng Thng, Bn Cho Vay c th
gi in v/hoc nhn tin cho Bn Vay v/hoc cc s in thoi khc yu cu Bn Vay thanh ton.
3. Cam kt v bo m
3.1. Trong thi gian c hiu lc ca Hp ng Tn Dng, Bn Vay c trch nhim ngay lp tc thng bo cho
Bn Cho Vay bng in thoi v bng th tn bt k thay i no v cc thng tin cung cp cho Bn
Cho Vay. Trng hp khng nhn c thng bo ca Bn Vay, Bn Cho Vay mc nhin hiu rng cc
thng tin ny khng c thay i v Bn Cho Vay c quyn s dng cc thng tin ny trong cc ti liu
ca Bn Cho Vay ph hp vi quy nh php lut.
Bn Vay hiu v ng rng, trong trng hp c s khc bit thng tin ca Bn Vay th hin trn
Ngh Cp Tn Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T v/hoc Hp ng Tn Dng v giy
t do Bn Vay cung cp, Bn Cho Vay c quyn cp nht/iu chnh thng tin trn Ngh Cp Tn
Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T v/hoc Hp ng Tn Dng ph hp vi thng tin
trn cc giy t v cc Bn khng cn phi k vn bn iu chnh thng tin.
3.2. Bn Vay m bo v cam kt s dng Khon Cp Vn theo ng mc ch s dng vn vay theo Ngh
Cp Tn Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T v Hp ng Tn Dng v chp hnh s
kim tra, gim st ca Bn Cho Vay trong qu trnh vay vn, s dng vn vay v tr n vay.
3.3. Bn Vay khng chuyn nhng hoc chuyn giao bt k quyn v/hoc ngha v no pht sinh t
Ngh Cp Tn Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T v Hp ng Tn Dng m khng c
s ng trc bng vn bn ca Bn Cho Vay.
3.4. Trong trng hp Bn Vay vi phm ngha v thanh ton v/hoc bt k iu khon no ca Ngh Cp
Tn Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T v/hoc Hp ng Tn Dng, Bn Vay ng

rng Bn Cho Vay c quyn s dng cc bin php v th tc php l cn thit ph hp vi quy nh php
lut hin hnh yu cu Bn Vay thanh ton cc Khon N theo quy nh ti Hp ng Tn Dng, bao
gm nhng khng gii hn (i) Bn Cho Vay c thc hin quyn i n i vi ton b ti sn m Bn
Vay c quyn s hu ti bt k ni no khc; (ii) Bn Vay ng v y quyn khng hy ngang cho Bn
Cho Vay ngh cc t chc tn dng ni Bn vay m ti khon, trch tin t ti khon ca Bn vay,
thanh ton Khon N cho Bn Cho Vay theo th tc ph hp vi quy nh ca t chc tn dng .
3.5. Bn Vay hiu v ng rng Bn Vay c trch nhim bo mt v khng tit l cho bn th ba bit S
Hp ng cng nh cc thng tin lin quan n Ngh Cp Tn Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch
V in T v Hp ng Tn Dng.
3.6. Tt c cc thng tin, ti liu Bn Vay cung cp cho Bn Cho Vay l chnh xc, hp php v khng c
thng tin no b che giu hoc b lm sai lch.
3.7. Trong mi trng hp, vic Bn Cho Vay khng thc hin quyn thu hi n theo quy nh ti Hp ng
Tn Dng s khng b xem l t b quyn thu hi n v khng cn tr Bn Cho Vay thc hin quyn thu
hi n ny vo bt k thi im no trong tng lai theo quy nh php lut v Bn Vay c ngha v thanh
ton y Khon N ngay sau khi Bn Cho Vay c yu cu theo Hp ng Tn Dng.
4. Thng tin ca Bn Vay
4.1. Bn Vay phi lp tc thng bo vi Bn Cho Vay bng in thoi v bng th tn trong trng hp c bt
k s kin no xy ra c th c nh hng bt li n nng lc thc hin ngha v tr n ca Bn Vay
theo quy nh ca Hp ng Tn Dng.
4.2. Vo bt k thi im no cho n khi hon thnh vic thanh ton Khon N, Bn Cho Vay c quyn kim
tra s y v chnh xc ca cc thng tin do Bn Vay cung cp, bao gm c kh nng Bn Cho Vay c
th s dng cc ngun iu tra c lp.
4.3. Trong thi gian c hiu lc ca Hp ng Tn Dng, Bn Cho Vay c th thu thp v s dng cc d liu
thng tin c nhn ca Bn Vay nhm mc ch thc hin Hp ng Tn Dng v nhm cc mc ch
khc, bao gm (i) vic Bn Cho Vay thng tin, cho bn n Bn Vay cc sn phm, dch v ti chnh
mi, cc thng tin qung co, khuyn mi ca Bn Cho Vay Bn Vay c c thng tin v c hi
tham gia vo cc sn phm, dch v ny; v (ii) i chiu v thu thp thng tin ca Bn Vay trn cc trang
mng x hi. Bn Cho Vay c th lu tr cc d liu thng tin nu trn di cc hnh thc ph hp vi
quy nh ca php lut.
4.4. Bn Cho Vay c quyn tin hnh cc bin php x l i vi cc li khai sai lch hoc bt thng
chng gian ln v la o.
5. Thng Bo
5.1. Tt c cc thng bo v cc thng tin khc (Thng Bo) m Bn Cho Vay cung cp cho Bn Vay c
th c (i) lp thnh vn bn v gi qua ng bu in n a ch Bn Vay cung cp theo quy nh ti
Ngh Cp Tn Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T v/hoc Hp ng Tn Dng hoc
giao tn tay Bn Vay; hoc (ii) gi di dng th in t; hoc (iii) c cung cp qua in thoi; hoc
(iv) gi di dng tin nhn. Bn Cho Vay c min tr mi trch nhim lin quan trong trng hp Bn
Vay khng nhn c Thng Bo t Bn Cho Vay do thng tin a ch hoc th in t hoc s in thoi
Bn Vay cung cp cho Bn Cho Vay khng chnh xc hoc thay i nhng Bn Vay khng thng bo
cho Bn Cho Vay theo quy nh ti Hp ng Tn Dng.
5.2. Bn Cho vay c quyn s dng mt trong cc phng thc nu ti Mc 5.1 ca Bn iu Khon V iu
Kin Chung thng bo cho Bn Vay cc ni dung bao gm nhng khng gii hn v vic chuyn n
qu hn; chm dt cho vay, thu hi n trc hn, v cc ni dung khc pht sinh trong qu trnh thc
hin Hp ng Tn Dng.

4
5.3. Mi Thng Bo c gi theo mt trong cc phng thc quy nh ti Mc 5.1 ca Bn iu Khon V
iu Kin Chung ny c xem l nhn bi Bn Vay: (i) vo ngy lm vic th ba k t ngy gi i
bng ng bu in hoc vo ngy giao tn tay; (ii) vo ngy Bn Vay nhn c in thoi ca Bn
Cho Vay; (iii) vo ngy Bn Cho Vay gi tin nhn hoc th in t cho Bn Vay.
5.4. Thng Bo m Bn Vay cung cp cho Bn Cho Vay c th c lp theo mt trong cc phng thc nu
ti Mc 5.1 v Thng Bo c xem l nhn bi Bn Cho Vay nh quy nh ti Mc 5.3 ca Bn iu
Khon V iu Kin Chung ny, tr trng hp quy nh khc trong Hp ng Tn Dng v/hoc cc
tho thun khc gia Bn Vay v Bn Cho Vay.
6. Khiu ni v thng tin tn dng ca Bn Vay
Trong trng hp Bn Vay khiu ni v thng tin tn dng ca Bn Vay lin quan n Ngh Cp Tn
Dng Kim Tha Thun S Dng Dch V in T v/hoc Hp ng Tn Dng, vic khiu ni phi
c lp bng vn bn v gi bng th in t hoc ng bu in cho Bn Cho Vay, trong nu r
l do km theo cc ti liu, chng c chng minh ni dung khiu ni v cc ti liu lin quan khc. Trong
trng hp Bn Cho Vay yu cu Bn Vay b sung thng tin gii quyt khiu ni, Bn Vay c ngha
v cung cp thng tin, ti liu lin quan theo thng bo ca Bn Cho Vay. Bn Cho Vay ch xem xt gii
quyt khiu ni ca Bn Vay sau khi nhn c khiu ni hp l theo quy nh ni b ca Bn Cho
Vay v quy nh php lut. Nu Bn Vay khng hoc cha cung cp y v kp thi ti liu, chng c
chng minh ni dung khiu ni v/hoc Bn Cho Vay vn ang trong qu trnh xc minh lm r v vic,
Bn Cho Vay vn tin hnh cc th tc php l cn thit lin quan n nghip v thu v x l n theo quy
nh ni b ca Bn Cho Vay v quy nh ca php lut. ng thi, thng tin tn dng ca Bn Vay vn
c Bn Cho Vay cung cp cho Trung Tm Thng Tin Tn Dng Quc Gia Vit Nam (CIC) theo quy
nh php lut.
